attributes.body:
With a starting potency of well over 85% cannabinoids, the Elite cartridge is perfect for the moderate to seasoned cannabis enthusiast. We add terpenes with mild sweet, spicy and sour notes to our signature distillate to produce Golden Goat. This cart offers a full-bodied, lively daytime cannabis sativa flavor experience. 


These cartridges use medical-grade ceramic atomizers that provide low failure rates, even draw distribution, no burning taste, and more vapor delivered per draw.

KulluKush 1 Gram Tank - Strawberry Shortcake
attributes.body:
Introducing the Kullukush 1 gram Tank in the Strawberry Shortcake strain from Multitude Manufacturing. This tank is filled with a premium filtered distillate with over 90 percent THC potency and infused with a custom blend of live and botanical terpenes. KulluKush tanks are designed to provide you with a convenient and enjoyable cannabis experience. It's the pinnacle of potency and quality with the Kullukush Tank in the high-end I-Krusher ceramic reservoir.

Known for its potent euphoric effects, this tank offers a delightful combination of pungent, fruity, and creamy vanilla flavors. With each puff, you'll experience a smooth and flavorful vapor that captures the essence of this popular strain.
